00:14:24,468 --> 00:14:27,163
我要去厕所了
I'm going to go to the bathroom.

348
00:14:27,468 --> 00:14:30,881
我猜 就我一个人了吧
By myself, I guess.

349
00:14:30,882 --> 00:14:33,117
小心有熊
Watch out for bears.

350
00:14:36,654 --> 00:14:41,325
既然今晚可能会是最后的一晚了 我得坦白一些东西
Since this might be the end, I gotta confess something.

351
00:14:41,326 --> 00:14:42,326
可以么
Can I?

352
00:14:42,327 --> 00:14:43,894
请便
Might as well.

353
00:14:43,895 --> 00:14:48,332
在过去的一段时间里
Barney and I have been doing the wild thing...

354
00:14:48,333 --> 00:14:50,934
除掉去年巴尼和马修的妈妈鬼混的一小段时间
this whole time.

355
00:14:50,935 --> 00:14:53,804
我和巴尼
Except a brief period last year when he was shacking up

356
00:14:53,805 --> 00:14:55,573
经常滚床单
with Marshall's mom.

357
00:14:55,574 --> 00:14:59,176
幸运的是 3P已经提上了日程 所以
But luckily, three-ways were on the menu, so...

358
00:14:59,177 --> 00:15:02,113
马修 你知道她没说那些 是吧
Marshall, you know she didn't say any of that, right?

359
00:15:02,114 --> 00:15:05,616
是的 但我就是想狠狠的抽他
I know, but I just want to slap him so bad!

360
00:15:05,617 --> 00:15:08,919
但这个领带看上去蠢透了 但我还是很想扇他
But that tie is so stupid! But the slap would feel so good!

361
00:15:08,920 --> 00:15:10,854
但他恨透了这条领带
But he hates that tie so much!

362
00:15:10,855 --> 00:15:13,090
或许我可以帮上一些忙
Perhaps I can help.

363
00:15:13,091 --> 00:15:16,893
马修 问问自己这个问题 为什么是今天
Marshall, ask yourself this question: why today?

364
00:15:19,097 --> 00:15:21,432
他整整憋了几个星期没去抱怨这条领带
He hasn't said anything about that tie for weeks,

365
00:15:21,433 --> 00:15:23,033
一直到 今天
and yet, suddenly today,

366
00:15:23,034 --> 00:15:24,935
他就不能再戴着这条领带多一秒么
he can't wear it another second?

367
00:15:26,037 --> 00:15:27,704
不 因为这其中必然有隐情
No, there's a reason.

368
00:15:27,705 --> 00:15:29,373
你一定隐藏了一些什么
You've got something coming up.

369
00:15:29,374 --> 00:15:31,475
一些你不想说出来
Something where you're

370
00:15:31,476 --> 00:15:34,845
显得自己处于弱势
on display, vulnerable...

371
00:15:34,846 --> 00:15:35,912
并暴露自己的事情
exposed.

372
00:15:37,782 --> 00:15:39,183
这跟工作无关
It's not work-related.

373
00:15:39,184 --> 00:15:41,619
哦 这一定是跟情感挂钩的
No, this is relationship stuff.

374
00:15:41,620 --> 00:15:44,388
你一定是想让某些人对你印象深刻
You're trying to impress someone.

375
00:15:44,389 --> 00:15:45,756
在你开篇撒的那个谎中
In the lie you told,

376
00:15:45,757 --> 00:15:47,724
你说你被两个傻子追着
you said you were being chased by two goons.

377
00:15:47,725 --> 00:15:49,092
所以是两个人
So it's two people.

378
00:15:49,093 --> 00:15:50,628
可能是一对情侣
A couple, perhaps.

379
00:15:52,130 --> 00:15:55,366
你明天要去见诺拉的父母
You're meeting Nora's parents tomorrow!

380
00:15:55,367 --> 00:15:57,834
不对
Wrong!

381
00:15:57,835 --> 00:15:59,936
错 错 错 错 错
Wrong, wrong, wrong, wrong, wrong!

382
00:15:59,937 --> 00:16:03,240
是两天后 我真的希望他们能够喜欢我
It's in two days, and I really want them to like me!

383
00:16:03,241 --> 00:16:05,176
哦 理疗师般的推理
Oh-ho! Therapisted!

384
00:16:05,177 --> 00:16:06,810
该说心理医师的推理 
Shrinked? Shrunk?

385
00:16:06,811 --> 00:16:08,011
我回头会弄清楚的
We'll figure it out.

386
00:16:08,012 --> 00:16:09,680
那么 趴板冲浪
So, boogie-boarding.

387
00:16:09,681 --> 00:16:10,981
嗯 趴板冲浪
Boogie-boarding.

388
00:16:10,982 --> 00:16:14,818
嘿 莉莉 我能和你说几句话么
Hey, Lily, can I talk to you for just a second?

389
00:16:15,953 --> 00:16:17,454
来
Come here.

390
00:16:17,455 --> 00:16:20,791
马修 如果你让我来帮你刷牙 我发誓...
Marshall, if I'm in here to brush your teeth, I swear to...

391
00:16:22,093 --> 00:16:24,495
很抱歉 最近我这么黏人
I'm sorry that I've been so needy lately.

392
00:16:24,496 --> 00:16:26,730
我知道 你需要一些独处的时间
I know that you need some time alone.

393
00:16:26,731 --> 00:16:29,600
那么 我去别的房间了
So... I'll be in the other room.

394
00:16:30,768 --> 00:16:32,703
你哪儿也不用去
You're not going anywhere.

395
00:16:34,239 --> 00:16:37,208
嗯 嘿
Mmm... Hey...

396
00:16:39,511 --> 00:16:41,412
有趣的是
And the funny thing is,

397
00:16:41,413 --> 00:16:44,481
自从那晚上之后 我们永远都不会一个人了
after that night, we'll never be alone again.

398
00:16:44,482 --> 00:16:46,617
你们在我的浴室里尽情的翻滚了
You made that in my bathroom?

399
00:16:46,618 --> 00:16:49,019
哇哦
Whoops.

400
00:16:49,020 --> 00:16:51,822
哇 一个飓风孩子
Wow, a hurricane baby.

401
00:16:51,823 --> 00:16:54,658
哇哦 伙计 艾瑞克森 飓风 可是个好名字
Oh, man, Hurricane Eriksen would be a sweet name.

402
00:16:54,659 --> 00:16:56,594
这是个爆好的名字啊
It would be a crazy sweet name!

403
00:16:56,595 --> 00:16:58,629
谢谢了您呐  泰德
Thanks, Ted.

404
00:16:58,630 --> 00:17:01,532
不管怎么说 第二天危险过去了
Anyway, the next day, after the danger had passed...

405
00:17:01,533 --> 00:17:03,900
关门了
It's closed.

406
00:17:03,901 --> 00:17:04,901
现在怎么说
Now what?

407
00:17:04,902 --> 00:17:07,904
童子军总是有所准备的
A Boy Scout is always prepared.

408
00:17:07,905 --> 00:17:09,906
嘿
Hey!

409
00:17:09,907 --> 00:17:12,409
好样的
Nice!

410
00:17:12,410 --> 00:17:13,677
为我们在飓风中幸存下来 干杯
To surviving the hurricane.

411
00:17:13,678 --> 00:17:14,678
耶
Yay!

412
00:17:14,679 --> 00:17:17,715
-我爱你们   -我也爱你
-I love you guys.   -Love you.

413
00:17:17,716 --> 00:17:20,451
那周晚些时候我才回到了公寓
I did finally make it up here to the house later that week

414
00:17:20,452 --> 00:17:22,586
发现一颗倒了的橡树
only to find that a falling oak tree had

415
00:17:22,587 --> 00:17:24,154
压在了客厅里
landed in the living room.

416
00:17:24,155 --> 00:17:27,090
如果我们在那儿的话 会被像虫子一样被压死的
If we'd been here, it would have crushed us like bugs.

417
00:17:27,091 --> 00:17:29,426
看到没有 孩子们 永远没有办法知道
You see, kids, there's no way of knowing for sure

418
00:17:29,427 --> 00:17:30,927
哪儿才是最安全的地方
where the safest place is...

419
00:17:30,928 --> 00:17:34,431
所以最好的期望就是 找到一些好伙伴
so the best you can hope for is to have some good company.

420
00:17:34,432 --> 00:17:36,767
伙计们 你们猜我用这个当滑板冲浪能冲多远
Guys, how far do you think I can boogie-board on this thing?

421
00:17:36,768 --> 00:17:38,201
心有多远你就能冲多远
So far!

422
00:17:38,202 --> 00:17:41,171
马修 你的医保要到明天才能生效
Marshall, your insurance doesn't kick in till tomorrow.

423
00:17:41,172 --> 00:17:43,407
无所谓
Yeah, well, you know what?

424
00:17:43,408 --> 00:17:44,975
享受生活从这一刻就生效了
Life kicks in right now.

425
00:17:54,786 --> 00:17:56,353
别担心 他没伤着
Don't worry, he wasn't hurt...

426
00:17:56,354 --> 00:17:58,155
当然 那是第一次冲得时候 我有急救夹板
the first time. I have splints!

427
00:17:58,156 --> 00:18:00,491
第二次嘛 他直接穿过了酒吧的窗户
The second time he went through the front window of Maclaren's.

428
00:18:00,492 --> 00:18:02,793
就是现在放着 严禁爬版冲浪标志的地方
Hence the "No Boogie-boarding" Sign.

429
00:18:02,794 --> 00:18:04,928
好的 伙计们 我要走了
All right, guys, I gotta go.

430
00:18:04,929 --> 00:18:07,665
巴尼 祝你见诺拉父母时好运
Barney, good luck with Nora's parents.

431
00:18:07,666 --> 00:18:08,666
-拜   -拜
Bye.   -Bye.

432
00:18:08,667 --> 00:18:09,667
再见
See you later.

433
00:18:09,668 --> 00:18:11,635
-好的 再见   -再见
-All right. See you.   -See ya.

434
00:18:12,870 --> 00:18:13,970
嘿 巴尼
Hey, Barney?

435
00:18:13,971 --> 00:18:14,871
嗯
Hmm?

436
00:18:14,872 --> 00:18:16,907
听着 我们在你的浴室
Listen, um, we made a baby

437
00:18:16,908 --> 00:18:18,509
造出了宝宝
in your bathroom.

438
00:18:18,510 --> 00:18:20,010
所以我们欠你个人情
So we owe you one.

439
00:18:21,245 --> 00:18:23,246
所以我们认为
So we say...

440
00:18:23,247 --> 00:18:25,382
你可以拿掉那个鸭子领带
you can take off the ducky tie.

441
00:18:27,452 --> 00:18:29,787
代价是再被我扇三巴掌
For three slaps.

442
00:18:29,788 --> 00:18:31,655
三巴掌
Three slaps?

443
00:18:31,656 --> 00:18:34,491
事先澄清一下 是追加三巴掌
And to be clear, this would add three slaps

444
00:18:34,492 --> 00:18:38,161
加上之前剩下的一个 一共是四巴掌
to Marshall's existing one, giving him four slaps in total.

445
00:18:38,162 --> 00:18:38,995
成交
Deal.

446
00:18:41,966 --> 00:18:43,266
我自由了
I'm free!

447
00:18:43,267 --> 00:18:47,170
天啊 这感觉太好了
God, this feels so good!

448
00:18:47,171 --> 00:18:49,873
不 这是个错误
This was a mistake!

449
00:18:49,874 --> 00:18:51,241
我想戴回领带
I wanna put the tie back on!

450
00:18:51,242 --> 00:18:52,476
给我那条领带
I wanna put the tie back on!

451
00:18:52,477 --> 00:18:54,044
为什么我要在现在变回原来的巴尼
Why do I have to be Barney right now?

452
00:18:56,280 --> 00:18:57,715
还剩三个耳光
Three slaps remaining!

453
00:18:57,716 --> 00:19:00,016
三个耳光 哇哦 我喜欢这声音
Three slaps. Wow, I like the sound of that.

454
00:19:00,017 --> 00:19:01,819
我觉得我可以挽救这些坏蛋
I think I'll save those bad boys,

455
00:19:01,820 --> 00:19:03,286
你懂得 以备不时之需
you know, for a rainy day.

456
00:19:03,287 --> 00:19:04,888
好吧 最坏的已经过去了
Okay. The worst is over.

457
00:19:06,891 --> 00:19:07,991
啊
Ah!

458
00:19:07,992 --> 00:19:10,527
还剩两个耳光
Two slaps remaining!

459
00:19:12,163 --> 00:19:13,397
我还好
It's all right.

460
00:19:13,398 --> 00:19:15,332
嘿 已经结束了
Hey, it's all done...

461
00:19:15,333 --> 00:19:16,633
只是现在哟
for now.

462
00:19:16,634 --> 00:19:18,435
我觉得我要回家了
I think I need to go home

463
00:19:18,436 --> 00:19:20,637
去重新评估我该如何做各种人生决定
and reevaluate how I make life decisions.

464
00:19:20,638 --> 00:19:22,939
来吧 我要回去工作了
Come on. I have to go back to work.

465
00:19:22,940 --> 00:19:25,008
我们拼车吧 好吧 恩
Let's split a cab. Okay. Yeah.

466
00:19:30,548 --> 00:19:35,819
你告诉过那些家伙另外一件
Did you ever tell those guys about that other thing

467
00:19:35,820 --> 00:19:37,220
差点发生的事吗
that almost happened?

468
00:19:37,221 --> 00:19:41,191
另外一件事
That other thing?

469
00:19:41,192 --> 00:19:42,926
哦 那个啊 没 呢
Oh, that. No. Did you?

470
00:19:42,927 --> 00:19:44,194
没
No.

471
00:19:45,430 --> 00:19:47,330
关于那个电话我很抱歉
Hey, I'm really sorry about that phone call.

472
00:19:47,331 --> 00:19:48,399
哦 还好
Oh, it's fine.

473
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:50,834
不 那不好 我就是个混蛋
No, it is so not fine. I was a jerk.

474
00:19:50,835 --> 00:19:52,836
如果你不在意的我的说法 你爸爸没打电话
And if you don't mind my saying, your dad is

475
00:19:52,837 --> 00:19:55,873
他就是一个十足的蠢蛋
a complete idiot for not calling.

476
00:19:55,874 --> 00:19:58,542
他应该每天都给你打电话的
He should never let a day go by without calling you

477
00:19:58,543 --> 00:20:02,613
因为我要是有一天没有跟你说话
because when I let a day go by without talking to you...

478
00:20:02,614 --> 00:20:08,419
额 那一天就过的不好
Um, that day's just no good.

479
00:20:13,024 --> 00:20:15,125
额 不好意思
Um, sorry.

480
00:20:15,126 --> 00:20:16,427
额
Um...

481
00:20:17,462 --> 00:20:19,129
那是我爸爸
It's my dad.

482
00:20:19,130 --> 00:20:20,263
等一下 让我看看你的手
Wait, show me your hands.

483
00:20:20,264 --> 00:20:21,298
啥都没有
My hands.

484
00:20:21,299 --> 00:20:24,200
嘿 爸爸
Hey, Dad!

485
00:20:24,201 --> 00:20:26,937
那就是我一直都在说的
That's what I've been saying!

486
00:20:26,938 --> 00:20:28,806
高尔夫天气
Golf weather!

487
00:20:28,807 --> 00:20:30,507
你能相信我们差点就
Can you believe we almost...?

488
00:20:30,508 --> 00:20:32,075
我知道
I know.

489
00:20:32,076 --> 00:20:33,143
我们没做的好事
Good thing we didn't.

490
00:20:33,144 --> 00:20:35,245
恩 我是说 那不久之后
Yeah. I mean, not long after that

491
00:20:35,246 --> 00:20:36,613
你跟诺拉在一起了
you got together with Nora.

492
00:20:36,614 --> 00:20:37,781
你也遇见了凯文
And you met Kevin.

493
00:20:37,782 --> 00:20:38,882
恩 灾难避免了
Yeah. Disaster averted.

494
00:20:38,883 --> 00:20:40,183
确实是
Exactly.

495
00:20:40,184 --> 00:20:42,252
如果我们这么做了会毁掉一切的
It would've ruined everything if we'd been all...

496
00:20:42,253 --> 00:20:43,226
啊 啦啦啦
ah-la-la-la...

497
00:20:43,346 --> 00:20:45,355
我知道 对的 那太白痴了
I know, right? So dumb...

498
00:20:45,356 --> 00:20:47,816
啦啦啦啦啦
La-la-la-la-la-la...

499
00:20:49,761 --> 00:21:00,704
（whoa 欢呼的BR党们）

